- `/home/denis/Workspaces/hackathon/spectopus/src/pipeline/model.js` - Core model export; all pipeline stages import from here; first file to change
- `/home/denis/Workspaces/hackathon/spectopus/src/tools/research.js` - Tool definitions; `inputSchema` → `schema`, dict → array export, add `name` fields
- `/home/denis/Workspaces/hackathon/spectopus/src/pipeline/research.js` - Primary fix target; replace broken `generateText+maxSteps` with `createReactAgent`
- `/home/denis/Workspaces/hackathon/spectopus/src/pipeline/validate.js` - Two `generateText` call sites to replace with `model.invoke()`; test mock also needs updating
- `/home/denis/Workspaces/hackathon/spectopus/package.json` - Add `langchain`, `@langchain/openai`, `@langchain/langgraph`, `@langchain/core`; remove `ai`, `@ai-sdk/openai`

